  <Document>
    <name>BASECAMP — 1906 Alpine Club of Canada Camp</name>
    <description>Places, routes and camps from the first ACC camp at Yoho Pass, July 1906. Extracted from Canadian Alpine Journal Vol.1 No.1.</description>
